news.title: Prestige Group to invest Rs 7,500 crore to develop 16 million sq ft in Mumbai
news.para: “With the state recording the highest GST collections in India and contributing to 15% of GST of the overall Indian economy, Mumbai has established itself as the leading commercial hub in India. We look forward to establishing our presence in the western region through Mumbai,” Irfan Razack, CMD, Prestige Group, told ET.

news.title: MDDA to take action on over 600 illegal structures identified in Dehradun
news.para: In a meeting of senior agency officials with state minister Premchand Aggarwal on Friday, instructions were given to the staff to speed up steps against illegal construction.

news.title: Telangana HC stops apartment association from taking coercive action against owners
news.para: A vacation bench of the Telangana high court has issued a notice to an apartment association asking it to explain its stand on a petition filed by some flat owners questioning the action of the association stopping essential services to them.
